Package: TExpress
Title: Tools for Analyzing Transposable Element (TE) Expression
Version: 1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Guillermo", "Peris", , "peris@uji.es",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2010-7844"))
Description: Provides a complete workflow for the downstream analysis of
    transposable element (TE) expression from TElocal count tables. The package
    performs differential expression analysis with DESeq2, annotates TEs by their
    genomic context relative to protein-coding genes, and classifies them as
    self-expressed or gene-dependent, together with publication-ready plots.
